
                                            Twitter users agree President Jacob Zuma just can't catch a break after being dealt the latest legal blow.
                                         JOHANNESBURG - If anyone knows about taking an "L" (slang for suffering a loss), it's President Jacob Zuma, according to South Africans on Twitter. Zuma had one of his worst days in court on Wednesday after the Pretoria High Court dismissed his bid to review the State Capture report and ordered him to personally pay the costs. 